quran[8{c,v,t}:
16,103,hamein maloom hai yeh log tumahray mutaliq kehte hain ke is shakhs ko aik aadmi sakata paratha hai halaank un ka ishara jis aadmi ki taraf hai is ki zabaan ajmi hai aur yeh saaf arabi zabaan hai
16,104,haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log Allah ki ayaat ko nahi mantay Allah kabhi un ko sahih baat taq pounchanay ki tofeq nahi deta aur aisay logon ke liye dard naak azaab hai
16,105,"( jhooti baatein naya nahi ghurr taa balkay ) jhoot woh log ghurr rahay hain, jo Allah ki ayaat ko nahi mantay, wohi haqeeqat mein jhutay hain"
16,106,jo shakhs imaan laane ke baad kufar kere ( woh agar ) majaboor kya gaya ho aur dil is ka imaan par mutmaen ho ( tab to kher ) magar jis ne dil ki Raza mandi se kufar ko qubool kar liya is par Allah ka ghazab hai aur aisay sab logon ke liye bara azaab hai
16,107,"yeh is liye ke onhon ne akhirat ke muqaabla mein duniya ki zindagi ko pasand kar liya, aur Allah ka qaida hai ke woh unn logon ko raah nijaat nahi dekhata jo uss ki Nemat ka kufran karen"
16,108,yeh woh log hain jin ke dilon aur kaanon aur aankhon par Allah ne mohar laga di hai yeh ghaflat mein doob chuke hain
16,109,zaroor hai ke akhirat mein yahi khasaray mein rahen
16,110,"bakhilaf is ke jin logon ka haal yeh hai ke jab ( imaan laane ki wajah se ) woh sataye gay to onhon ne ghar baar chore diye, hijrat ki, raah khuda mein sakhtiyaan jhelen aur sbrse kaam liya, unn ke liye yaqeenan tera rab ghafoor o Raheem hai"
